Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
set_metric_header(25.10)                              set_metric_header(25.10)

Name
       set_metric_header - Sets the name of a metric header

Syntax
       set_metric_header

       [-id <db_id>]

       -name <header_name>

       -help

       -value <header> <_value>

       Sets the name of a metric header.

Parameters
       -id <db_id>
              Specifies the database ID.

              Data_type: string, optional

       -name <header> <_name >
              Specifies the name of the header.

              Data_type: string, required

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each set_metric_header parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man set_metric_header

       -value <header> <_value>
              Specifies the value of the header.

              Data_type: string, required

Related Information
              * delete_metric_header

              * get_metric_header

